import React, { useEffect } from "react"
import { makeStyles } from '@material-ui/core/styles'
import Container from '@material-ui/core/Container'
import Box from '@material-ui/core/Box'
import Grid from '@material-ui/core/Grid'
import Button from '@material-ui/core/Button'
import Chip from '@material-ui/core/Chip'
import IconButton from '@material-ui/core/IconButton';
import Icon from '@material-ui/core/Icon';
import CloseIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Close';
import Typography from '@material-ui/core/Typography'
import Avatar from '@material-ui/core/Avatar'
import Divider from '@material-ui/core/Divider'

const useStyles = makeStyles({
  root: {
    position: 'relative',
    display: 'inline-block',
    width: '500px',
    background: "white",
    boxShadow: '0 0 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.25), 0 0 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.22)',
    zIndex:10,
    overflow: 'auto',
  },
  hide: {
    display: "none",
  },
  closeButton: {
   position: 'absolute',
   right: 5,
   top: 5,
   color: "grey",
 },
 image: {
   width: "100px",
   height: "100px"
 },
 topImage: {
   width: "100%",
   height: "200px",
   objectFit: "cover"
 },
});

const Midbar = props => {
  const classes = useStyles()

  return (
    <Box px={6} className={props.showMidbar ? classes.root : classes.hide}>

      <Box display="flex" flexDirection="column" alignItems="center">
        <Box mt={4}>
          <Avatar src={'/therapist-images/' + props.therapist.image} className={classes.image}/>
        </Box>

        <Box fontSize="24px" mt={3}>
          {props.therapist.name} {props.therapist.surname}
        </Box>

        <Box color="textSecondary">
          Couples therapist
        </Box>

        <Box pt={2}>
          <Button variant="contained" color="secondary">Email</Button>
          <Button variant="contained" color="secondary">Website</Button>
        </Box>
      </Box>

      <Box py={1.5}>
        <Box fontSize="12px" color="secondary">About {props.therapist.name}</Box>
        <Box>
          30 Years of private practice. Masters of Social Work from University of Georigia. Licensed Clinical Social Worker
        </Box>
      </Box>

      <Box py={1.5}>
        Specialty Areas
        <Box>
          Depression, Anxiety, Stress, Marriage
        </Box>
      </Box>

      <Box py={1.5}>
        Treatment Approaches
        <Box>
          Emotionally-Focused Therapy, Cognitive Behavioral Therapy
        </Box>
      </Box>

      <Box py={1.5}>
        Payment
        <Box>
          $180 per session
        </Box>
      </Box>

      <Box py={1.5}>
        Type
        <Box>
          Individuals, Families
        </Box>
      </Box>


      <IconButton aria-label="close" className={classes.closeButton} onClick={() => props.setShowMidbar(false)}>
        <CloseIcon />
      </IconButton>


    </Box>
  )

}

export default Midbar
